[thinking] I’m thinking about how to handle Internet Explorer options and whether we need the second set. It looks like the name "MapsAndCapabilities" isn't quite right. Also, I wonder if setting invalid capabilities needs some validation. A potential fix could be asserting that the source retains its values after setting nested capabilities. However, I realize that I may not be testing the API's effects properly with this approach. It's quite a complex situation!
[thinking] 
[assistant-event] thinking_end
